Effect file formats:
- Luxinia shaders: http://www.luxinia.de/index.php/Api/Shader
- Ogre materials: http://www.ogre3d.org/docs/manual/manual_14.html#SEC23
- Hyperion shaders (o3shd) and effects (xml): www.oZone3D.Net
- glfx: http://glfx.sourceforge.net/
- pyfx: http://graphics.cs.lth.se/pyfx/
- unity shaders: http://www.unifycommunity.com/wiki/index.php?title=Shader_Archive
- Collada FX: http://www.khronos.org/collada/

